e":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54ab9401b4140ff6c7ca5f5589e5e2a36b975e2","tid":713843,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e58c38772d3e9d9d78de1caa169aa05da2fa379c","tid":713843,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"白雲雞"},{"pid":"1f93408f41375af5686a6f10ed829a00576144a3","tid":713843,"uid":95519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"搵野食apps:大眾點評<br />\n<br />\n唱K: 堂會<br />\n<br />\n食：<br />\n<ins> 天河南一路</ins><br />\n一龍拉麵（日式）[強烈推介]<br />\n米倉食堂（偏日式）<br />\n厝内小眷村（台式）<br />\n煮餃（中式）<br />\n<br />\n<ins>正佳廣場</ins><br />\n瑞可爺爺的店嘅岩燒乳酪<br />\n<br />\n<ins>廣州東東方寶泰</ins><br />\n泰萊（泰式）<br />\n<br />\n<ins>獵德</ins><br />\n點都德（中式/粵式）<br />\n<br />\n<ins>江南西</ins><br />\n簡悅廚Coolinmint<br />\n<br />\n<ins>上下九</ins><br />\n南信雙皮奶<br />\n<br />\n<ins>公園前/北京路</ins><br />\n北京路步行街<br />\n<br />\n<ins>農講所</ins><br />\n百花甜品店<br />\n婆婆麵（中式）<br />\n食盈碗仔翅<br />\n<br />\n<ins>荔灣公園</ins><br />\n係艇上面食艇仔粥<br />\n<br />\n<ins>西門口</ins><br />\n六嬸西關小廚<br />\n<br />\n<ins>黃沙</ins><br />\n海鮮<br />\n<br />\n注意：<strong> 唔好係大陸食牛扒，你會後悔</strong><br />\n<br />\n玩：<br />\n廣州塔<br />\n動漫星城扶手電梯底夾公仔（容易夾中）<br />\n沙面影西式教堂<br />\n上下九步行街/黃埔古港影舊式建築<br />\n譚村泰式按摩Spa<br />\n荔灣公園<br />\n白雲山"},{"pid":"62877b534eb7839ba3d5b0eb041f5d1c6b7df75c","tid":713843,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無睇到落雨都去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去夾下公仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626010ffdd48c4e0e2b0984b6e4f6b778a3ba564","tid":713843,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep